# Derived scoring artifacts are large (several GB each) and reproducible
# from data/derived/<cohort>/*_summary.tsv via `thermocas score-cohort`.
# Do not commit. History was rewritten on 2026-04-20 to drop the prior
# commits of these artifacts; see the [Unreleased] CHANGELOG entry and
# ../thermocas-framework-pre-rewrite.bundle (local byte-for-byte backup).
data/derived/scored_*.jsonl
data/derived/catalog_*.jsonl

# Transient build logs from cohort builders.
data/derived/*_build.log

